Package: semEffect
Title: Structural Equation Model (SEM) Effects Analysis and Visualization
Version: 1.0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Weiping", 
	family = "Mei", 
	role = c("aut", "cre"),
	email = "meiweipingg@163.com", 
	comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6400-9862"))
Description: This package calculates direct, indirect, and total effects for a target variable in a SEM model. It supports visualization of effects through bar plots and includes automated dependency checks.
URL: https://github.com/PhDMeiwp/semEffect/
